Package simzombie.engine.graph

Class Summary
Graph The Graph class contains a series of data points.
GraphCanvas An extension of JPanel supplied to display a representation of a Graph object
Plot Contains basic information about a plot (data series, x and y locations, colour)
Plot.PlotComparator Compares a plot based on the X axis alone This allows us to organise our plots from left to right, for display purposes
PrinterFriendly Class containing information on which printer friendly options are available for graphs and how to draw them
 

Enum Summary
GraphCanvas.LegendPosition Toggles to display the Legend on the east and south of the graph
PrinterFriendly.PrinterFriendlyOption Potential printer friendly options for a data series
